{"tid":792376,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英入稟控鍾劍華及立場新聞誹謗","createTime":"2018-08-24T13:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T05:57:23.000Z","uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1e1a5faa8cd18cee24a8d1d1e090a685b8e6d6de","tid":792376,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T13:36:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=317870\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D317870&d=SJV3gE3fh1%2BrfClmsDzY21KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=b6ffa91d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D317870&h=acff3626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=317870</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】前行政長官梁振英入稟，控告理大學者鍾劍華以及立場新聞誹謗。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英在社交網站發文，稱已委託律師入稟高等法院，控告理大應用社會科學系助理教授鍾劍華及立場新聞誹謗。<br />\n<br />\n他指，港人有言論及新聞自由，但同時有免被誹謗的權利，罔顧事實中傷他人的人應該受到法律制裁。<br />\n<br />\n帖文亦連結了梁振英早前發出律師信，指鍾劍華在立場新聞發表的一篇文章，提及梁振英與江湖人物有關係，屬於失實指控，要求刪除文章及公開道歉。"},{"pid":"0ba35c56c0cc659755a57aece753c1458511b045","tid":792376,"uid":42767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T14:17:29.000Z","msg":"哲學題: 梁振英作為黨和國家領導人, 法律地位上係咪凌駕於司法機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c00ed7bdad9e98739d8e157ec05aa39ef506e3b","tid":792376,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:48:19.000Z","msg":"捐咗 $100 去守護公議基金<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bxzmFS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bxzmFS</a>"},{"pid":"99a80d081eb2fd7d7a44970ef029d5da3fd310de","tid":792376,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:57:23.000Z","msg":"鍾劍華之前仲牙斬斬，依家又要眾籌？"}]}